# Next Slide

The shiki Javascript library provides beautiful syntax highlighting.
To use this highlighter, specify beforeInit: ["https://unpkg.com/shiki", "shiki-addon.js"] in nature and include shiki-addon.js at same folder as your rmd file.
The theme can be changed in shiki-addon.js with avaliable themes are listed here.
